          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Desktop: body paragraph (hidden on mobile via CSS) -->
      <p class="rc-education__body">
        Based on your delivery location, we have identified 25 harmful contaminants in your local water supply. Tap water can contain contaminants and forever chemicals such as lead, PFAS and arsenic even when it meets local regulations.
      </p>

      <!-- Mobile: Learn more with arrow (hidden on desktop via CSS) -->
      <a href="#" class="rc-education__link rc-education__link--mobile">
        <span>Learn more</span>
        <span class="rc-education__link-arrow">&rarr;</span>
      </a>

      <!-- Desktop: Learn more > underlined (hidden on mobile via CSS) -->
      <a href="#" class="rc-education__link rc-education__link--desktop">Learn more &gt;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</script>
